OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FSunshine and showers for Saturday,
OL,7,Fwith the blustery winds easing
OL,8,Fovernight. Generally dry on Saturday
OL,9,Fand Sunday, with patchy cloud and
OL,10,Fsunny spells. Feeling warm, especially
OL,11,Fin the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
